{"tid":2517309,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中年廚師被控堵路及藏有雷射筆罪成 判監八個月","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:44:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2f53661499d041c948e70e14cbf1dd7f05c4c3","tid":2517309,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15474&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn9kum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=5ae81ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15474</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第十四庭 <br />\n#黃士翔裁判官 <br />\n#1112荃灣 #判刑 #阻街 #攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n甄(48)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)在公眾地方造成阻礙 <br />\n(2)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1)被控於2019年11月12日，在荃灣沙咀道239號外，無合理辯解或合法權限，與其他人以聚集方式，對上述公眾地方的道路造成阻礙<br />\n(2)被控於同日同地無合理辯解或合法權限，攜有攻擊性武器，即3個能發出鐳射光束的裝置<br />\n<br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<br />\n裁決按此 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15170&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn9kum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=5e3c9b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15170</a>)👈🏿<br />\n<br />\n速報：<br />\n控罪一：一個月監禁<br />\n控罪二：八個月監禁<br />\n所有刑期同期執行<br />\n<br />\n詳情後補"},{"pid":"d6a968d8c592eaebe8a9aa7b5c23ef58576d51a3","tid":2517309,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45706a26bd23b373ef9ad4a22ae22a839bddbf58","tid":2517309,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"荒謬"},{"pid":"463fb4ea7d98843299008f7210b7e8a2931c232b","tid":2517309,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"至於管有攻擊性武器罪，裁判官指案情嚴重之處在於被告管有3支雷射筆，可供他人使用；而其中一支達第四級，可在100米外對視力造成損害或<span class=\"red\">釀成火災</span>，另外兩支亦達3B級別，故就此判囚8個月。兩罪刑期同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n不如講放大鏡啊笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/HKSW3B6ZVNBCFMFNIKB7X3ASMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2FHKSW3B6ZVNBCFMFNIKB7X3ASMU%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn9kum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=65f4c807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2FHKSW3B6ZVNBCFMFNIKB7X3ASMU%2F&h=9cbd79f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/HKSW3B6ZVNBCFMFNIKB7X3ASMU/</a>"},{"pid":"9481bf079888696bc2025d2b0927ad8fbe117373","tid":2517309,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"裁判官認為，本案嚴重之處在於被告不單止攜帶一支鐳射筆，而是 3 支，換言之除自用外，亦可供給他人使用。再者，該些鐳射筆分別屬第 3B 及 4 級，可致眼角膜受損，甚至釀成火災。雖然無證據顯示被告曾分發鐳射筆予他人使用，但考慮到整體環境，決定判囚 8 個月。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/11-12-%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%BB%9A%E5%B8%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-8-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%AE%98-%E9%99%A4%E8%87%AA%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%AF%E7%B5%A6%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F11-12-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BB%259A%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-8-%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BB%259